<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_3991d93b-0747-4fc8-89eb-91464ebdd3d3" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="VIC"><sptc>E1D6</sptc><title id="_1d6302dd-12c9-4e13-be58-d330e4430942">Where sprinklers are required: Class 2 and 3 buildings other than residential care buildings</title><subclause id="_6cd685f5-a382-4817-bae9-40842cb69789" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e3662e05-e8dc-4071-b594-cb12b0eff8e6">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Sprinklers are <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_a082fdfb-82b3-45bf-85d7-414af0e29e0b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> throughout—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_0042fbbb-ebbd-4f86-ab75-a0123cd0218e">A <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/8156_0.5.0.xml#_8ae20f35-99b1-4b61-b8d1-9bf91f64ed81" id="_aaa81d4b-d7bf-4068-bb78-72a5666ecfef" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">shared accommodation building</xref>; and</li><li id="_963d30bc-0f65-4d8f-b2f5-cb07d9bd167c">In a Class 2 or 3 building, or any multi-classified building containing a Class 2 or 3 part, if any part of the building has—<ol><li>a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1439_5.1.0.xml#_7023b962-6482-412b-8416-ab1d9016072b" id="_2605c3e4-955e-40b8-9008-3cdd01c82724" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">rise in storeys</xref> of 4 or more; and</li><li>an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1252_2.0.0.xml#_cd986c21-bc64-43a9-954d-86e35d335b74" id="_15a09bcf-3af8-4dce-b2b6-38251171c1e1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">effective height</xref> of not more than 25 m.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_18452098-6b4b-4a0c-87e7-73d9760a383a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_501df913-2643-4baf-8ff1-9603c2a65ccd">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The requirements of (1) do not apply to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_9d016284-8990-4f06-b303-5e53f52019dc">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/10629_0.3.0.xml#_5ab30347-b491-4403-b95c-dba5ab5d9aec" id="_5fe45fdd-cef6-465f-ad49-65c8d74cb2d6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">residential care building</xref>; and</li><li id="_6a082061-040f-4744-aa6d-d4f19b812670">a Class 8 <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1255_0.4.0.xml#_7a37df1f-0b8b-4b03-94ca-69ea423a363f" id="_61c15b4e-c50c-45e7-a17a-4f3027b4b4cb" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">electricity network substation</xref> with a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_4b5b7a90-56fb-44c1-a3d0-055f9ca47219" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> not more than 200 m<sup id="_6e791e50-4971-487e-bb59-8b9d7be01ff3">2</sup> located within a multi-classified building.</li></ol></subclause></clause>